<h2>What is the USVI?</h2>

<p>The USVI consists of 3 small isalnds barly visible on the map. St.Croix, St.thomas and St.John 
<Img src="https://www.gotostcroix.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/edit_top-10-reasons-to-choose-st-croix_caerial-caribbean.jpg>
St.Croix is the biggest of the islands, known for its argucluture vast "virgin" land and it seems almost as if ir were frozen in time with its older architucture.








